<frame cBy="JKR" cDate="08/23/2002 02:47:50 PDT Fri" name="Forgiveness" ID="401" xsi:schemaLocation="../schema/frame.xsd" xmlns="http://framenet.icsi.berkeley.edu" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
    <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;A &lt;fen&gt;Judge&lt;/fen&gt; refrains from imposing, or demanding a punishment for an &lt;fen&gt;Evaluee&lt;/fen&gt; who has committed an &lt;fen&gt;Offense&lt;/fen&gt;. 
&lt;ex&gt;&lt;fex name="Judge"&gt;God&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;forgives&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="Evaluee"&gt;repentant sinners&lt;/fex&gt;.&lt;/ex&gt;
&lt;ex&gt;Won't &lt;fex name="Judge"&gt;you&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;forgive&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="Evaluee"&gt;me&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;fex name="Offense"&gt;for keeping it a secret&lt;/fex&gt;?&lt;/ex&gt;&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
    <FE bgColor="FF0000" fgColor="FFFFFF" coreType="Core" cBy="JKR" cDate="08/23/2002 06:16:41 PDT Fri" abbrev="Judge" name="Judge" ID="3610">
        <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;The &lt;fen&gt;Judge&lt;/fen&gt; holds the &lt;fen&gt;Evaluee&lt;/fen&gt; responsible for the &lt;fen&gt;Offense&lt;/fen&gt;.&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
        <semType name="Sentient" ID="5"/>
    </FE>
    <FE bgColor="00008B" fgColor="FFFFFF" coreType="Core" cBy="JKR" cDate="08/23/2002 06:17:06 PDT Fri" abbrev="Evaluee" name="Evaluee" ID="3611">
        <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;The &lt;fen&gt;Evaluee&lt;/fen&gt; is subject to the judgment of the &lt;fen&gt;Judge&lt;/fen&gt; for having committed the &lt;fen&gt;Offense&lt;/fen&gt;.
&lt;ex&gt;&lt;fex name="Judge"&gt;God&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;forgives&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="Evaluee"&gt;repentant sinners&lt;/fex&gt;.&lt;/ex&gt;&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
    </FE>
    <FE bgColor="006400" fgColor="FFFFFF" coreType="Core" cBy="JKR" cDate="08/23/2002 06:17:47 PDT Fri" abbrev="Offense" name="Offense" ID="3612">
        <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;The &lt;fen&gt;Offense&lt;/fen&gt; is the illicit or unpleasant act committed by the &lt;fen&gt;Evaluee&lt;/fen&gt;.
&lt;ex&gt;Won't &lt;fex name="Judge"&gt;you&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;forgive&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="Evaluee"&gt;me&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;fex name="Offense"&gt;for keeping it a secret&lt;/fex&gt;?&lt;/ex&gt;&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
    </FE>
